{"tid":2368234,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「天荒夜談」有無人摸索到自己基因入面有咩能力遺傳俾到自己？","createTime":"2021-01-16T04:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T17:47:48.000Z","uid":141237,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3d283046a89bb221f251bc457ca2f6e7dc17ae","tid":2368234,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"近幾年發現自己模仿能力算係幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係只會係點到即止，即係做俾旁人睇可能以為你係pro，但係俾真係pro既人睇好容易就穿煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗返以前仲係荒野求生存既祖先，會唔會係靠依種能力去生存而將依種能力從基因入面遺傳到俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8bde3081d950b1421250b5933590fb3550a46b","tid":2368234,"uid":2974,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"一日可以訓16個鐘"},{"pid":"9ffc5a90f36e0d9d81afb8a5aaedd48cd0997e95","tid":2368234,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f8bde3081d950b1421250b5933590fb3550a46b","tid":2368234,"uid":2974,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"一日可以訓16個鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"唔通你祖先以前係靠避世而生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa65ee7b5365d3711d21aa92b0268efec7ca9bd","tid":2368234,"uid":64884,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"眼力好好<br />\n講緊3 4歲已經開始打機到而家都冇近視"},{"pid":"ad27870667dc9bcfe9c5f642cc74969eeb9c8323","tid":2368234,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"識捲脷"},{"pid":"9d8da60f186396df561769c8854db1310d9cf9e2","tid":2368234,"uid":141237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6aa65ee7b5365d3711d21aa92b0268efec7ca9bd","tid":2368234,"uid":64884,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-